b'Tabisuru Nuigurumi: Traveling Daru': b'Daru, a cherished handmade stuffed toy, gets lost and separated from its owner one day when at the airport. Determined to find her again, Daru sets out on a journey around the world in search of her. As time passes, the girl begins to forget about Daru. Will Daru be able to find and see his beloved owner again?\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)'
